      "label": "home_body",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "This demo has three Views: home, projects, and detail. The home view auto-activates because it is first in the views list. Clicking Projects fires navProjects → a navigate wire on the root machine calls ViewSystem.navigate('projects') → the view:projects event fires → a pipeOut wire auto-loads the project list. Clicking a card calls ViewSystem.navigate('detail', { id, title, ... }) directly, pushing ?view=detail&id=1&title=... to the browser URL and routing you to the detail view.",
      "parentId": "M5",
      "children": [],
